description.narrative: This activity (Rule of Law Programme) is a component of Helmand Rule of Law reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £2,089,598. This component benefits Afghanistan, and works in the following sector(s): Legal and judicial development, Civilian peace-building, conflict prevention and resolution. The start date is 01-05-2008 and the end date is 31-03-2012.
